axis: residual-forwarding-nested-handlers
status: pending-runtime
needs: unhandled-operation forwarding from an inner handler to an outer handler
measured: with an inner `handle` over effect `Rd` nested inside an outer `handle`
  over effect `Wr`, performing `Wr.wr` inside the inner scope gives
  `ssc: match: no arm for wr/2` on portable-VM (2026-07-14) — the inner handler does
  not forward the unhandled `Wr` operation to the enclosing handler.
expected: an operation with no arm in the nearest handler is FORWARDED to the next
  enclosing handler (§14.1 "residual forwarding"; core §4 nested prompts). Handlers
  authored on either side must compose.
